data.description: Come see the amazing views across this scenic Live Oak Park Road property.  This spectacular locale is host to a spacious main house (3 bedrooms and “new” 2-1/2 baths) with a modern architecture feature and an open floor plan that been extensively remodeled with zone a/c and heating. House had 22 solar panels installed 2 years ago that will be paid off at closing. Enjoy a custom chef’s kitchen with matching Bosch appliances and wall mounted pot filler over the commercial grade gas range.  There is enough granite counter space and cabinets to meet all your culinary and storage needs.  Additionally, a detached dwelling (185 sqft) is adjacent to the main home with a bedroom, closet, full bath, new hot water heater and living area that would make a great guest room, office or game room.  The main house and detached flat are both surrounded by outdoor living areas and a custom led-lighted spillway water feature where you can enjoy the picturesque views.  You can sit under the large fully covered patio and a separate lanai with solar patio lighting that covers a 6 person above ground spa.  Across the property’s 4-1/2 acres there are approximately 300 Hass avocado trees in your own private grove.  Also planted, are several established and producing orange, lemon, lime, nectarine, peach, apple, guava, mango, and pomegranate trees throughout the grove to embrace a diverse planting strategy so you can enjoy something all year round.  In addition to the trees, there are 20 blueberry bushes, blackberries, and grapes.  The property has its own well, so water is never an issue as you enjoy caring for your own private grove.  Connected from the main house is a three-car carport and detached workroom and laundry, for the property’s small commercial reverse osmosis system that purifies the well water for the whole house and detached flat. The property exists on both sides of Live Oak Park Road.  Approximately ½ acre is across the street from the main lot with a beautiful “all year” natural stream bed (it is where the well is located).  The remaining 4 acres are fully fenced and gated, perfect for all pets/animals.  Enjoy camera-ready views from every corner of the property, which you can easily walk or drive around on the 4-wheel drive Gator or commercial grade tractor.  The barn is currently being used as an indoor chicken coop but has a solar operated door that opens/closes automatically to a large, completely fenced outdoor range.  There are eight laying hens included if you want them.  Experience the life of small-scale grove/farming with your own water, solar power, and very modern and comfortable accommodations.  The spa, John Deere tractor, wood-chipper, and 4-wheel drive Gator all convey.  A beautiful property in a beautiful location.  This property is not to be missed.
